{"tid":391160,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"白痴求教，三文魚扒應該點煎？","createTime":"2017-09-07T14:40:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-08T01:36:22.000Z","uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0af2ee2fe0ff708366ed00a2700b34174ad46b16","tid":391160,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T14:40:27.000Z","msg":"我得個易潔鑊夠未？三文魚應該唔駛咁熱啦，調味應該落啲乜？配菜用乜好？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bb7f815adb4afbfd195172058bc32049e2b84a1","tid":391160,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T14:43:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fba3805f6c1c5d87dfb0f2887b37c2ed85757cd5","tid":391160,"uid":72608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T14:44:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用車煎呀？駛乜撚嘢？</blockquote><br />\nC-"},{"pid":"1b669f5e48d2ff33764b45dc19fa6634fc6d8178","tid":391160,"uid":46754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T14:44:55.000Z","msg":"睇gordan ramsay"},{"pid":"033aee255c7e07bceed491ba7644b36c207c33bd","tid":391160,"uid":117009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T14:46:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SQuyOwNtAVM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DSQuyOwNtAVM&d=Oob3F8YH%2FrSR4mjBHCHhgL%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=ed7ae385\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SQuyOwNtAVM</a>"},{"pid":"8ee35487fe63fc3481dd28858777fd95702b32ff","tid":391160,"uid":78666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T14:46:12.000Z","msg":"乜柒都唔駛<br />\n落油之後就咁加少少鹽<br />\n煎香佢已經好好食"},{"pid":"7942970d56306fb5b92d5ee67ebf527691ae0a12","tid":391160,"uid":123204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T14:48:33.000Z","msg":"好容易overcook 就鞋<br />\n所以好少買黎煮<br />\n大火落鑊轉中細火 <br />\n唔好太老<br />\n<br />\n原味<del>hea</del>主意<br />\n落少少海鹽/食前加檸檬汁"},{"pid":"d47447c3d62b818f06226cf8ef61ad8b7a4f5fec","tid":391160,"uid":21364,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T15:00:20.000Z","msg":"其實三文魚依家野，同海鮮一樣，靚嘅唔洗搞咁多調味，鹽同黑白椒就ok，最多加啲Rosemary番茜，甚至喺超市買支Season $4X~6X一支就搞掂，只有肉質差嘅先要搞花臣，所以咁樣不如慳啲錢去Citysuper或者其他出口店買勁靚三文魚扒返屋企整仲好啦"},{"pid":"f948367890447342dc8d2caced62c992ec8418ef","tid":391160,"uid":31022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T15:09:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實三文魚依家野，同<span style=\"color: red;\">牛排</span>一樣，靚嘅唔洗搞咁多調味，鹽同黑白椒就ok，最多加啲Rosemary番茜，甚至喺超市買支Season $4X~6X一支就搞掂，只有肉質差嘅先要搞花臣，所以咁樣不如慳啲錢去Citysuper或者其他出口店買勁靚三文魚扒返屋企整仲好啦</blockquote>"},{"pid":"55fb2cdc7a5966ce95dbfdc849b4341797ba6e8b","tid":391160,"uid":140736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T17:39:48.000Z","msg":"紅燒汁中火，反轉再大火<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6181a85fcff19a6af7d82d1fd19dc7b848c9ebe","tid":391160,"uid":126046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T01:30:57.000Z","msg":"魚洗下佢 抹乾 落少少鹽<br />\n開爐 燒紅隻鑊 落油<br />\n油熱 有紋 可以落魚<br />\n先煎魚皮<br />\n唔駛點郁佢 由佢煎 兩分鐘左右<br />\n郁吓隻鑊 舊魚冇痴就反轉佢<br />\n繼續煎 煎到咁上下 <br />\n加一舊仔牛油 溶咗用隻匙 北啲油上層皮度<br />\n煎多一分鐘左右<br />\n熄火 落檸檬汁 加少少香草 (optional)<br />\n再用餘溫煎一分鐘左右<br />\n食得 趁熱食<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n時間視乎舊魚厚薄 自己執生"},{"pid":"7ac18e8dc02720e81d5549328df80cbad8e0fca6","tid":391160,"uid":1096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T01:36:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>魚洗下佢 抹乾 落少少鹽<br />\n開爐 燒紅隻鑊 落油<br />\n油熱 有紋 可以落魚<br />\n先煎魚皮<br />\n唔駛點郁佢 由佢煎 兩分鐘左右<br />\n郁吓隻鑊 舊魚冇痴就反轉佢<br />\n繼續煎 煎到咁上下 <br />\n加一舊仔牛油 溶咗用隻匙 北啲油上層皮度<br />\n煎多一分鐘左右<br />\n熄火 落檸檬汁 加少少香草 (optional)<br />\n再用餘溫煎一分鐘左右<br />\n食得 趁熱食<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n時間視乎舊魚厚薄 自己執生</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}